<view class="page home-page"><view class="home-top-wrapper"><view class="home-top-bg"></view><view class="home-top-content"><view class="card home-header"><view class="home-header-left"><view class="hello-text"> 你好， <text wx:if="{{a}}">{{b}}</text><text wx:else>患者朋友</text></view><view class="hello-sub">今天是 {{c}}，请按提示完成今日监测和康养指标。</view></view><view class="home-header-right"><view class="{{e}}">{{d}}</view></view></view><view class="card task-card"><view class="card-title-row"><view class="card-title">今日任务</view><view class="card-sub">已完成 {{f}} / 2 项</view></view><view class="task-row"><view class="task-left"><view class="task-title">今日自测</view><view class="task-desc">血压、体温、症状等基础监测，建议每天完成 1 次。</view></view><view class="{{h}}">{{g}}</view></view><view class="task-row"><view class="task-left"><view class="task-title">今日康养指标</view><view class="task-desc">4 步康养指标填报，记录症状、睡眠、用药、运动与饮食等情况。</view></view><view class="{{j}}">{{i}}</view></view><view class="task-actions"><button class="btn-outline" bindtap="{{k}}" hover-class="btn-hover">开始今日自测</button><button class="btn-outline" bindtap="{{l}}" hover-class="btn-hover">填写康养指标</button></view></view></view></view><view class="home-bottom"><view class="{{['card', 'lab-tip-card', s]}}" bindtap="{{t}}"><view class="card-title-row"><view class="card-title">{{m}}</view><view class="{{o}}">{{n}}</view></view><view class="lab-tip-text">{{p}}</view><view wx:if="{{q}}" class="lab-tip-meta">{{r}}</view></view><view class="card quick-card"><view class="card-title-row"><view class="card-title">监测与数据</view><view class="card-link" bindtap="{{v}}">全部</view></view><view class="quick-row center"><view class="quick-item tongue-only" bindtap="{{w}}" hover-class="quick-item-hover"><view class="quick-icon">👅</view><view class="quick-text">舌象采集</view></view></view></view></view></view>